      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  In particular, it describes managed objects used for managing dial-up modems and similar dial-up devices. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
